            <title>[SOLR-367] RFC: use contrete return types in analysis factory declarations</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-367</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;will attach patch for comments: the main idea is to change most of the Tokenizer and TokenFilterFactories to be explicit about what their &quot;create&quot; method returns instead of just using &quot;TokenStream&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
